author: @claudioc.
content: It was a historic concert, but out of context, as it took place at a time when Brazil was going through a climate tragedy involving dozens of deaths and thousands of homeless people due to unprecedented flooding... I like this singer, but I think it was a big mistake for her to hold this event!
